OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome early brightness this
OL,6,Fmorning, though becoming generally
OL,7,Fcloudy and windy today with some
OL,8,Fshowery outbreaks of rain developing,
OL,9,Fthis perhaps turning heavy at times.
OL,10,FStrong southwesterly winds developing,
OL,11,Fwith gales likely in coastal and
OL,12,Fupland regions. Mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FVery wet and windy this
OL,15,Fevening with some heavy rain. Clearer
OL,16,Fskies arriving overnight. Turning
OL,17,Fcolder, though staying largely frost-
OL,18,Ffree. Perhaps the odd wintry shower on
OL,19,Fhigh ground. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
